OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FYesterday, the boss of the world's
OL,8,Flargest oil company, Aramco, warned of
OL,9,F"catastrophic consequences" if the war
OL,10,Fdrags on.
OL,12,FToday, the chancellor was asked what
OL,13,Fsupport she might offer businesses and
OL,14,Fhouseholds already feeling the strain,
OL,15,Fnot least when filling up the car.
OL,17,F"Nothing is off the table," she told
OL,18,FMPs.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@[O]yD@AOUyD@[O]
