FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773324683
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FAt first glance, that sounds enormous.
OL,9,FIn reality, it represents roughly a
OL,10,Fmonth's worth of oil flows that would
OL,11,Fnormally pass through the Strait of
OL,12,FHormuz.
OL,14,FAnd even that oil will not arrive
OL,15,Finstantly. It is still unclear which
OL,16,Fcountries will release what, and how
OL,17,Fquickly those barrels will actually
OL,18,Freach the market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773324683
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSome analysts say the scale of the
OL,8,Frelease suggests governments are
OL,9,Fpreparing for a prolonged disruption
OL,10,Frather than a short shock.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the ripple effects are
OL,13,Falready spreading through the global
OL,14,Feconomy.
OL,16,FThe price of jet fuel has jumped by
OL,17,Faround 50% in the past week. If that
OL,18,Fincrease persists, airlines will
OL,19,Feventually pass the cost on to
OL,20,Fpassengers through higher ticket
OL,21,Fprices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773324683
OL,3,CThe release of 400 million barrels of
OL,4,Coil is not enough to end the energy
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump has promised
OL,8,Fmilitary escorts for tankers and even
OL,9,Finsurance guarantees to encourage
OL,10,Fships back into the Gulf.
OL,12,FBut for now, shipping companies still
OL,13,Fsee the area as too dangerous to enter.
OL,15,FReleasing emergency oil stocks may
OL,16,Fhelp contain the surge in energy
OL,17,Fprices.
OL,19,FBut it does not solve the underlying
OL,20,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
